parameters:
\SE[41]Ehehe... I'm good at it. \!\SE[0]Everyone in the
village taught me...
\SE[86]My father... he even made me a knife...

Don't bear it all alone. \!\SM[nod]\SE[52]I'll be by your
side...

\SE[7]It's been such a long time since I last saw Luna...
\!\SE[1]You've become really cool. I was a little
surprised...
It's been five years... But, isn't that an exaggeration?

\SE[83]That's not true.... \!\SE[84]You looked like a prince
from a picture book....

\SE[29]Um, what should I call you...? \SE[90]'Luna'... it
sounds too childish, I'm sure... it's embarrassing,
right...?

\SE[0]... No, please, call me that. \SE[46] No matter how
much time passes... It's wonderful to have something that
doesn't change.
\SE[85]I-Is that so...? \SE[28]I-I see, then I'll do that...

Laura... you've become beautiful. \SE[15] At first, I wasn't
sure if I got it right.

\SM[jump]\SE[5]Me...? Oh, you must be joking...? \SE\SE[91]I
never grew taller at all, and \SE[91]I've never even had a
single confession...
It's not just that Laura hasn't noticed...?

For example... Have you ever been consulted about whether or
not to confess to someone you like...?

\SE[5]Ah... that might have happened a lot.... \SE[7]I
didn't really understand, but I'm cheering for you!
\SE[5]Please do your best! \SE[7]That's all I could say....

Have you ever been invited to have a meal together... or
something like that?

\SE\SE[22]Ah... I think there was. \SE[1]But my mom always
cooks for me, so \SE[22]it feels like a waste to eat
outside...

\SE\SE\SE[90]Ah, there it is! \. I wonder if it got blown
away by the wind? \!\SE\SE[90]But the warehouse keeper found
it for me... \!\SE[90]It was dirty, so they threw it away
for me...

\SE[2]Huh... what...? \SE[3]Is there something wrong with
that...?
Maybe all of those people... liked you.

\SE[21]Ahaha... Those people must have been pitiful....
\SE[0]Laura, wasn't it a waste for you too...?

\SE[3]Hmm... well, it's not really... I'm more concerned
about...

...I guess I talked a little too much. \!\SE[0]It's been a
while and it was fun...

\SE\SE[0]Let's get some rest for tomorrow, okay? \SE[0]We're
planning to travel a considerable distance...

\SE\SE[90]Ah... Yeah, I understand... \SM[nod]Is it okay if
I stay like this...?

Sleep peacefully, Laura... I will definitely protect you...
No matter how dirty my hands become... Only you... I will
always...
